family all the best

00:06:55.981 --> 00:06:57.817 align:start size:81% position:19% line:0%
during this
most difficult time.

00:06:57.917 --> 00:06:59.685 align:start size:75% position:25% line:0%
Thank you, Jamie.
Godspeed.

00:06:59.785 --> 00:07:02.121 align:start size:84% position:16%
