 He wants his voice back
 for his job.</i>

00:07:02.221 --> 00:07:05.391 align:start size:84% position:16%
<i> He desperately needs it
 back for his life.</i>

00:07:05.491 --> 00:07:08.928 align:start size:81% position:19%
