<i> (Jaye)
 In our interview,</i>

00:07:23.976 --> 00:07:25.945 align:start size:81% position:19%
<i> Dupree holds a marker
 between his teeth.</i>

00:07:26.045 --> 00:07:27.413 align:start size:78% position:22%
<i> It helps to control
 his tongue,</i>

00:07:27.513 --> 00:07:28.847
<i> so he can speak.</i>

00:07:28.948 --> 00:07:31.250 align:start size:84% position:16%
<i> To describe life
 as a husband and father</i>

00:07:31.350 --> 00:07:34.420
<i> who must fight
 for each word.</i>

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:38.724 align:start size:75% position:25%
Anyone who has children,

00:07:38.824 --> 00:07:41.660 align:start size:50% position:50%
you want to talk
to them,

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:47.466 align:start size:66% position:34%
and give them advice,
and help.

00:07:47.566 --> 00:07:53.738 align:start size:75% position:25%
