<i> (Jaye)
 He has learned to trick
 his misfiring brain.</i>

00:08:01.346 --> 00:08:04.149 align:start size:78% position:22%
Yeah, you know if I tried
to talk like a muppet,

00:08:04.250 --> 00:08:06.017 align:start size:56% position:44%
I can get
a little more out.

00:08:06.118 --> 00:08:08.053 align:start size:72% position:28%
<i> (Jaye)
 But it never
 works for long.</i>

00:08:08.153 --> 00:08:10.088 align:start size:84% position:16%
<i> There is one tiny area
 of his life</i>

00:08:10.188 --> 00:08:12.390
<i> that has improved.</i>

