00:16:48.073 --> 00:16:50.876 align:start size:91% position:9%
<i> and that's because similar
 regions in the brain,</i>

00:16:50.976 --> 00:16:54.446 align:start size:94% position:6%
<i> the hippocampus and the
 medial orbital frontal cortex</i>

00:16:54.546 --> 00:16:57.850 align:start position:0%
<i>are both involved in these
seemingly different activities.</i>

